{"word":"βοτήρ","slug":"βοτήρ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βοτήρ</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:βόσκω'><el>βόσκω</el></a>\n<p/><i>a herdsman, herd</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; <el>οἰωνῶν β.</el> <i>a soothsayer</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>; <el>κύων βοτήρ</el> a <i>herdsman's</i> dog, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/>"}]}